  "url": "https://www.nps.gov/grca/learn/nature/birds.htm",
  "title": "Birds - Grand Canyon National Park (U.S. National Park Service)",
  "html": "<body class=\"ParkSite\"><span aria-label=\"Top of page\" id=\"__topdoc__\" role=\"navigation\"></span>\n\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div id=\"beforeSkipLinks\" tabindex=\"-1\"></div>\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"GlobalHeader usaGlobalHeader\" role=\"banner\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"exitModalLabel\" class=\"modal refreshableModal\" id=\"myModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h2 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"exitModalLabel\">Exiting nps.gov</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\"></div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Schedule\" id=\"cs_control_481716\"><div id=\"CS_Element_BannerContainer\" title=\"\"><div class=\"cs_GridRow\" id=\"gridRow_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_GridColumn\" id=\"gridCol_1_1_1_1_481716\"><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_830326\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1951882_830326\">\n\n</div></div><div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_CustomCF\" id=\"cs_control_481855\"><div id=\"CS_CCF_1951882_481855\"> </div></div></div></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"Park-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"pull-left\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n\n</div>\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n\n<!--googleon: index-->\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div aria-label=\"Alerts Notification\" class=\"AlertsNotification\" data-site-code=\"grca\" id=\"AlertsNotification\" role=\"dialog\">\n<div aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"AlertsNotification__Status visually-hidden\" role=\"status\">Loading alerts</div>\n<div class=\"collapse\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Panel\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Header\">\n<h2 class=\"Tag\" id=\"AlertsNotificationHeading\">Alerts In Effect</h2>\n<button aria-label=\"Dismiss\" class=\"AlertsNotification__DismissButton\" type=\"button\">\nDismiss\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#close\"></use>\n</svg>\n</button>\n<span class=\"hr clearfix\"></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__Body\" id=\"AlertsNotificationBody\">\n<div class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLinkContainer\">\n<svg class=\"usa-icon\" focusable=\"false\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use href=\"/theme/assets/vendor/npsds/packages/icons/dist/sprite.svg#add\"></use>\n</svg>\n<a class=\"AlertsNotification__MoreLink\" href=\"/grca/planyourvisit/conditions.htm\" id=\"AlertsNotificationMoreLink\" tabindex=\"-1\">\nmore information on current conditions...\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"MainContent\" id=\"main\" role=\"main\">\n\n<div aria-labelledby=\"modal-contact-us-label\" class=\"modal fade\" id=\"modal-contact-us\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h4 class=\"modal-title visually-hidden\" id=\"modal-contact-us-label\">Contact Us</h4>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"adminTools\"></div>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"ColumnGrid row\">\n<!--googleoff: index-->\n<div class=\"container\">\n\n</div>\n<!--googleon: index-->\n<div class=\"ColumnMain col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"ContentHeader text-content-size\">\n<h1 class=\"page-title\">Birds</h1>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Layout\" id=\"cs_control_2\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"CS_Layout_Table\" id=\"cs_idLayout2\" summary=\"\" width=\"100%\"><tr class=\"CS_Layout_TR\"><td class=\"CS_Layout_TD\" id=\"cs_idCell2x1x1\">\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_825464\">\n<div class=\"Component ArticleTextGroup TextWrapped clearfix\">\nBecause of its wide variety of ecosystems, Grand Canyon National Park is home to an incredible diversity of bird life with nearly 450 species of birds.  In 2014, the Grand Canyon was designated as a <a href=\"/grca/learn/nature/globally-important-bird-area-dedication-2014.htm\" id=\"CP___PAGEID=5432192,globally-important-bird-area-dedication-2014.htm,14077|\">Globally Important Bird Area</a> to recognize the important role the park plays in protecting hundreds of bird species.\n</div></div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5453247\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5453247\">\n<div class=\"Component ListingGrid -large\">\n<ul class=\"row\">\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/nature/bird-checklists.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/nature/bird-checklists.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A photo of a book cover featuring a canyon wren.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/08A2C25F-1DD8-B71B-0BC7AC7F9C8936F6.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/08A2C25F-1DD8-B71B-0BC7AC7F9C8936F6.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nSpecies Checklists\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">Bird checklists for Grand Canyon National Park.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/nature/bird-of-concern.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/nature/bird-of-concern.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A close up photo of a California Condor's bald head surrounded by black feathers. \" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/07C49597-1DD8-B71B-0B44BD6F73564C45.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/07C49597-1DD8-B71B-0B44BD6F73564C45.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nBird Species of Concern\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">The Grand Canyon is a refuge for some of the rarest bird species in the world. </p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"https://science.nature.nps.gov/im/units/scpn/monitor/birds.cfm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'https://science.nature.nps.gov/im/units/scpn/monitor/birds.cfm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A very small grey bird, a bush tit, at the tip of an evergreen tree.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/08F71588-1DD8-B71B-0B004B67F4C0C4DC.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/08F71588-1DD8-B71B-0B004B67F4C0C4DC.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nBird Community Monitoring\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">The Southern Colorado Plateau Network (SCPN) monitors the bird community in Grand Canyon's Mixed conifer forest,\nPinyon-juniper woodland</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/nature/birds-of-prey.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/nature/birds-of-prey.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A close-up shot of the dark hooded head of a peregrine falcon.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/07F85764-1DD8-B71B-0BF2A26F0D0CB780.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/07F85764-1DD8-B71B-0BF2A26F0D0CB780.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nBirds of Prey or Raptors\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">The Grand Canyon is an important location for raptor conservation efforts.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/nature/riparian-birds.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/nature/riparian-birds.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A black necked-stilt stands on the water's edge near the vegetation.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/9A05C3B9-1DD8-B71B-0B850B0C0F32A020.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/9A05C3B9-1DD8-B71B-0B850B0C0F32A020.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nRiparian Birds\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">The Colorado River and its dozens of tributary streams create important riparian habitat for many resident and migratory bird species. </p>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing\">\n<a class=\"ActivityListing-link\" href=\"/grca/learn/nature/other-birds.htm\" onclick=\"gas('send','event','Graphic Grid',document.location.href,'/grca/learn/nature/other-birds.htm',1,true)\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-imageContainer\">\n<img alt=\"A Pinyon Jay on the rim of the canyon with the canyon behind it.\" class=\"ActivityListing-image\" src=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/08483C21-1DD8-B71B-0B871834D3DCD328.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\" srcset=\"/common/uploads/grid_builder/grca/crop1_1/08483C21-1DD8-B71B-0B871834D3DCD328.jpg?width=640&amp;quality=90&amp;mode=crop\"/>\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-titleContainer\">\n<div class=\"ActivityListing-title\">\nOther Notable Birds\n<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fa fa-angle-right\"></i>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</a>\n<p class=\"ActivityListing-description\">The Grand Canyon is home to hundreds of important species which fill important ecological roles.</p>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_6628458\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_6628458\"> \n\n<div class=\"VideoHero\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/VideoObject\">\n<meta content=\"How Many Species Can You Spot?\" itemprop=\"name\"/>\n<meta content=\"This little watering hole in the courtyard at Grand Canyon Headquarters was all aflutter with activity during fall migration 2020. As birds make their way across the country, they look for safe places to drink and bathe before they continue on their way. Some species in this video are residents to this area year-round, while others are just passing through. We are so lucky to have so many awesome birds call Grand Canyon home!\" itemprop=\"description\"/>\n<meta content=\"T2M28S\" itemprop=\"duration\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/BC62DA2B-A7F5-21D8-9A22F4DC93424543/grca-BirdTimelapse-Rachel2_splash.jpg\" itemprop=\"thumbnailUrl\"/>\n<meta content=\"https://www.nps.gov/media/video/view.htm?id=BC62DA2B-A7F5-21D8-9A22F4DC93424543\" itemprop=\"embedURL\"/>\n<meta content=\"2020-10-14 00:00:00.0\" itemprop=\"uploadDate\"/>\n<div class=\"VideoHero-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin vjs-big-play-centered vjs-16-9\" controls=\"\" height=\"264\" id=\"av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543\" poster=\"/common/uploads/imr/park/grca/BFB8286E-D7B8-02AF-A70FC629890DC5DF/BFB8286E-D7B8-02AF-A70FC629890DC5DF-large.jpg\" preload=\"metadata\" width=\"640\">\n<source label=\"720p\" res=\"720\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/BC62DA2B-A7F5-21D8-9A22F4DC93424543/grca-BirdTimelapse-Rachel2_1280x720.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"480p\" res=\"480\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/BC62DA2B-A7F5-21D8-9A22F4DC93424543/grca-BirdTimelapse-Rachel2_854x480.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"360p\" res=\"360\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/BC62DA2B-A7F5-21D8-9A22F4DC93424543/grca-BirdTimelapse-Rachel2_640x360.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<source label=\"240p\" res=\"240\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/grca/BC62DA2B-A7F5-21D8-9A22F4DC93424543/grca-BirdTimelapse-Rachel2_426x240.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"/>\n<track kind=\"captions\" label=\"English\" src=\"https://www.nps.gov/nps-audiovideo/legacy/closed-caption/imr/avElement/grca-BirdTImelapseenUS2.vtt\" srclang=\"en\"/>\n</video>\n<button aria-disabled=\"false\" aria-live=\"polite\" class=\"vjs-embed-control vjs-button\" data-bs-target=\"#av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543EmbedModal\" data-bs-toggle=\"modal\" id=\"av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543EmbedButton\" title=\"Embed Video\" type=\"button\">Embed</button>\n<div aria-hidden=\"true\" aria-labelledby=\"av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543EmbedModalLabel\" class=\"modal fade VideoJSEmbedModal\" id=\"av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543EmbedModal\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered\">\n<div class=\"modal-content\">\n<div class=\"modal-header\">\n<h1 class=\"modal-title\" id=\"av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543EmbedModalLabel\">\nEmbed Video\n</h1>\n<button aria-label=\"Close\" class=\"btn-close\" data-bs-dismiss=\"modal\" type=\"button\"></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"modal-body\">\n<textarea class=\"form-control\" id=\"av_BC62DA2BA7F521D89A22F4DC93424543EmbedText\" rows=\"6\"></textarea>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"VideoHero-text\">\n<a class=\"VideoHero-videoLink visuallyhidden\" href=\"/media/video/keyboard-shortcuts.htm\">Visit our keyboard shortcuts docs for details</a>\n<dl class=\"result-details wrapped\">\n<dt>Duration:</dt><dd>2 minutes, 28 seconds</dd>\n</dl>\n<p itemprop=\"description\">This little watering hole in the courtyard at Grand Canyon Headquarters was all aflutter with activity during fall migration 2020. As birds make their way across the country, they look for safe places to drink and bathe before they continue on their way. Some species in this video are residents to this area year-round, while others are just passing through. We are so lucky to have so many awesome birds call Grand Canyon home!</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"CS_Layout_SpacingHeight\" id=\"cs_spacer_5460763\" style=\"line-height:1;\"> </div>\n<div class=\"cs_control CS_Element_Custom\" id=\"cs_control_5460763\">\n\n<div class=\"container ListingList ListingResults\" id=\"searchListing-D6F3E5A2-01A2-05F3-39AE96F484BE4118\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"results\">\n<a name=\"results\"></a>\n<div class=\"display-list-view\" id=\"display-list-view\">\n<div class=\"info-micro